<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 14:07:31 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>总理的妻子萨拉·内塔尼亚胡告诉人质家属，军队首长希望发动政变反对她的丈夫</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-25/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-wife-tells-hostage-families-idf-chiefs-want-to-stage-coup-against-her-husband/00000190-4f8c-d8cb-a19d-4fcf448c0000</link><description>在与少数人质家庭的一次小型会议上，总理的妻子一再表示她不信任军队领导人。代表内塔尼亚胡夫人的发言人表示，有关内塔尼亚胡夫人的虚假、有倾向性和持续的泄密行为构成了令人发指的不公正行为。</description><pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 13:55:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-25/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-wife-tells-hostage-families-idf-chiefs-want-to-stage-coup-against-her-husband/00000190-4f8c-d8cb-a19d-4fcf448c0000</guid></item><item><title>由于与真主党的紧张关系加剧，加拿大延长了以色列人的工作签证期限</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-25/ty-article/.premium/canada-extends-work-visa-deadline-for-israelis-due-to-rising-tensions-with-hezbollah/00000190-4f45-d3c0-a5d4-6f67eafd0000</link><description>以色列-哈马斯战争爆发后，加拿大最初于二月份向以色列人开放了签证计划，并提供三年期工作许可证，对职业或教育没有限制。截止日期原定于 6 月截止，但现已延长至 2025 年 7 月底</description><pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 13:34:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-25/ty-article/.premium/canada-extends-work-visa-deadline-for-israelis-due-to-rising-tensions-with-hezbollah/00000190-4f45-d3c0-a5d4-6f67eafd0000</guid></item><item><title>10 月 7 日以色列袭击事件受害者起诉近东救济工程处，指控其为哈马斯洗钱</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-25/ty-article/victims-of-oct-7-attack-against-israel-sue-unrwa-for-allegedly-laundering-money-for-hamas/00000190-4f5e-d768-adf8-4ffead600000</link><description>10 月 7 日哈马斯大屠杀的数十名受害者在一项诉讼中指控，近东救济工程处向哈马斯工作人员支付工资，并通过学校传播哈马斯的宣传，以此协助哈马斯。</description><pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 13:24:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-25/ty-article/victims-of-oct-7-attack-against-israel-sue-unrwa-for-allegedly-laundering-money-for-hamas/00000190-4f5e-d768-adf8-4ffead600000</guid></item><item><title>民意调查显示内塔尼亚胡的联盟受欢迎程度继续下降，斯莫特里奇退出议会</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-25/ty-article/.premium/poll-shows-netanyahus-coalition-continues-to-lose-popularity-smotrich-out-of-knesset/00000190-4e2b-da42-a1ba-7f6b8dd60000</link><description>Channel 12 的一项民意调查显示，在内塔尼亚胡的联盟党派中，阿耶·德里领导的沙斯党赢得了 10 个席位，联合托拉犹太教赢得了 8 个席位。虽然伊塔马尔·本·格维尔（Itamar Ben-Gvir）的政党获得了九个席位，但贝扎莱·斯莫特里奇（Bezalel Smotrich）的宗教犹太复国主义并未通过选举门槛</description><pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 12:49:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-25/ty-article/.premium/poll-shows-netanyahus-coalition-continues-to-lose-popularity-smotrich-out-of-knesset/00000190-4e2b-da42-a1ba-7f6b8dd60000</guid></item><item><title>以色列最高法院法官恢复探视监狱，但不会探视关押巴勒斯坦人的监狱</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-25/ty-article/.premium/israeli-top-court-justices-resume-prison-visits-but-wont-see-those-holding-palestinians/00000190-4f14-da42-a1ba-7f7e97800000</link><description>最高法院法官有权对所有监狱进行随机和预先安排的访问，以评估囚犯的关押条件。自加沙战争爆发以来，没有对关押巴勒斯坦囚犯的设施进行过此类参观</description><pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 12:47:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-25/ty-article/.premium/israeli-top-court-justices-resume-prison-visits-but-wont-see-those-holding-palestinians/00000190-4f14-da42-a1ba-7f7e97800000</guid></item><item><title>以色列最高法院“想要发动宗教战争”：正统MKs抨击对极端正统选秀的戏剧性裁决</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-25/ty-article/.premium/top-court-wants-to-force-religious-war-haredi-mks-blast-ruling-on-ultra-orthodox-draft/00000190-4ee9-d91c-abba-eff97d690000</link><description>高等法院一致裁决要求国家起草正统律法，引起了各个政治派别的强烈反应，一位政治家表示，“世界上没有任何力量可以阻止以色列人民学习托拉”，其他人则称该法院是“从民选政府手中夺取权力的独裁机构”</description><pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 11:28:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-25/ty-article/.premium/top-court-wants-to-force-religious-war-haredi-mks-blast-ruling-on-ultra-orthodox-draft/00000190-4ee9-d91c-abba-eff97d690000</guid></item><item><title>犹太人和阿拉伯人是这座以色列城市的好邻居。然后定居者带着枪出现</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-25/ty-article-magazine/.premium/jews-and-arabs-were-good-neighbors-in-this-city-then-settlers-showed-up-with-guns/00000190-4e8e-da42-a1ba-7fee2d330000</link><description>拜特谢安市的阿拉伯社区主要由与以色列安全部队合作的家庭组成。暴力右翼极端分子决定他们不能留在那里</description><pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 11:04:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-25/ty-article-magazine/.premium/jews-and-arabs-were-good-neighbors-in-this-city-then-settlers-showed-up-with-guns/00000190-4e8e-da42-a1ba-7fee2d330000</guid></item><item><title>警察局长：关于以色列的言论 警察越过了红线，我们不是民兵</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-25/ty-article/.premium/police-chief-discourse-on-israel-police-has-crossed-a-red-line-police-are-not-a-militia/00000190-4e9c-d8cb-a19d-4fdff4e10000</link><description>下个月结束任期的科比·沙卜泰表示，“警方不寻求对抗”，并承诺将对过度使用武力的案件进行调查。在加沙被扣押的人质兄弟：“当你的旗舰工具是水炮时，就会导致暴力”</description><pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 09:34:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-25/ty-article/.premium/police-chief-discourse-on-israel-police-has-crossed-a-red-line-police-are-not-a-militia/00000190-4e9c-d8cb-a19d-4fdff4e10000</guid></item><item><title>以色列最高法院规定国家必须征召极端正统派加入以色列国防军，这对内塔尼亚胡政府构成打击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-25/ty-article/.premium/in-blow-to-netanyahu-israels-top-court-says-state-must-draft-ultra-orthodox-to-army/0000018f-ed56-dc46-a5bf-fdd604e60000</link><description>经过多年的法律和政治争论，九名高等法​​院法官一致做出这一裁决，这将对内塔尼亚胡的执政联盟产生冲击波</description><pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 08:05:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-25/ty-article/.premium/in-blow-to-netanyahu-israels-top-court-says-state-must-draft-ultra-orthodox-to-army/0000018f-ed56-dc46-a5bf-fdd604e60000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡主义已经失败，现在正危及以色列的安全</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-25/ty-article/.premium/the-netanyahu-doctrine-has-failed-and-now-it-is-endangering-israels-security/00000190-4bdc-d8cb-a19d-4bdf46290000</link><description>一个误判就可能导致以色列和真主党陷入全面战争，造成大量平民伤亡。尽管美国发誓支持以色列，但它坚称不能保证从耶路撒冷的角度来看最佳结果</description><pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 03:00:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-25/ty-article/.premium/the-netanyahu-doctrine-has-failed-and-now-it-is-endangering-israels-security/00000190-4bdc-d8cb-a19d-4bdf46290000</guid></item><item><title>黎巴嫩最新火箭弹袭击导致以色列北部发生火灾</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-25/ty-article-live/blinken-stresses-need-for-post-war-gaza-plan-in-meeting-with-gallant/00000190-4d36-d768-adf8-4db68ad70000</link><description>报告：美国官员警告真主党不要认为自己能够阻止以色列袭击黎巴嫩 ■ 以色列国防军宣布，被绑架的以色列士兵于 10 月 7 日被杀，他的尸体被关押在加沙 ■ 内塔尼亚胡：“致力于拜登概述的以色列提议” ■ 以色列国防军杀死哈马斯弹药生产工作的关键人物 ■ 美国军方负责人表示，美国可能无法像对付伊朗那样保护以色列免受真主党的袭击</description><pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 02:46:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-25/ty-article-live/blinken-stresses-need-for-post-war-gaza-plan-in-meeting-with-gallant/00000190-4d36-d768-adf8-4db68ad70000</guid></item><item><title>解释：以色列的“潜艇事件”是什么？它会击沉内塔尼亚胡吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-25/ty-article/.premium/explained-what-is-israels-submarine-affair-and-could-it-sink-netanyahu/00000190-4c33-d8cb-a19d-4d73eee40000</link><description>国家调查委员会周一对所谓潜艇事件发出的警告信意味着什么？这些警告信是否会导致刑事调查？</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 21:56:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-25/ty-article/.premium/explained-what-is-israels-submarine-affair-and-could-it-sink-netanyahu/00000190-4c33-d8cb-a19d-4d73eee40000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡的潜艇警告信是以色列最大笨蛋的又一失败篇章</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-25/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-warning-letter-is-another-chapter-of-failure-for-israels-biggest-bungler/00000190-4bdc-d429-abfc-7bdee3520000</link><description>针对首相发出的警告信准确地描述了 10 月 7 日失败的序幕 - 以及从那一刻起随之而来的失败</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 21:28:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-25/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-warning-letter-is-another-chapter-of-failure-for-israels-biggest-bungler/00000190-4bdc-d429-abfc-7bdee3520000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军宣布被绑架的以色列士兵于10月7日被杀，其尸体被扣押在加沙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-24/ty-article/idf-announces-that-abducted-israeli-soldier-was-killed-on-oct-7-his-body-held-in-gaza/00000190-4b77-da60-a5b7-cfffb6b70000</link><description>中士。穆罕默德·阿特拉什少校是一名以色列国防军退伍军人，也是以色列国防军加沙分部的一名追踪员</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 20:45:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-24/ty-article/idf-announces-that-abducted-israeli-soldier-was-killed-on-oct-7-his-body-held-in-gaza/00000190-4b77-da60-a5b7-cfffb6b70000</guid></item><item><title>以色列儿童读物鼓励犹太人在黎巴嫩南部定居</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-06-24/ty-article/.premium/messianic-israelis-new-way-of-encouraging-settlement-in-south-lebanon-a-childrens-book/00000190-4ab3-da42-a1ba-7ffbefa00000</link><description>另外，7 月份参加耶路撒冷电影节的以色列电影、三位以色列摄影师反思了他们 10 月 7 日之后的作品以及歌手 Netta Barzilai 的新艺术方向</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 19:45:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-06-24/ty-article/.premium/messianic-israelis-new-way-of-encouraging-settlement-in-south-lebanon-a-childrens-book/00000190-4ab3-da42-a1ba-7ffbefa00000</guid></item><item><title>以色列向美国澄清，内塔尼亚胡的电视讲话并不反映加沙谈判立场的变化</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-24/ty-article/.premium/israel-tells-u-s-that-netanyahus-tv-remarks-dont-reflect-change-in-gaza-talks-stance/00000190-4b59-dafc-adb4-7bd9bffd0000</link><description>总理重申了之前的立场，并在议会讲话中澄清，他的政府“致力于拜登总统概述的以色列提案”</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 19:30:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-24/ty-article/.premium/israel-tells-u-s-that-netanyahus-tv-remarks-dont-reflect-change-in-gaza-talks-stance/00000190-4b59-dafc-adb4-7bd9bffd0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列即将与黎巴嫩真主党开战吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-24/ty-article/.highlight/will-there-be-a-third-lebanon-war-maybe-not-as-soon-as-you-think-or-sooner/00000190-4b14-d91c-abba-ef14ba030000</link><description>随着以色列国防军缩小加沙的战斗规模，以色列的注意力越来越集中在北部边境和真主党的威胁上。全面战争可能仍会发生，但双方目前也可能更愿意缓和局势</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 17:09:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-24/ty-article/.highlight/will-there-be-a-third-lebanon-war-maybe-not-as-soon-as-you-think-or-sooner/00000190-4b14-d91c-abba-ef14ba030000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡的一位盟友被任命为以色列新闻频道的负责人。它的记者不会不战而屈人之兵</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-24/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-journalists-fighting-the-selection-of-a-netanyahu-stooge-to-head-israeli-news-channel/00000190-49d7-d8cb-a19d-49d749d10000</link><description>任命尤利娅·沙马洛夫·贝尔科维奇为以色列第 13 频道负责人被视为内塔尼亚胡及其支持者将新闻媒体转变为右翼回声室的最新尝试。妇女团体对她过去有关性骚扰的言论感到震惊，已与记者一起努力推翻这一举措</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 17:00:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-24/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-journalists-fighting-the-selection-of-a-netanyahu-stooge-to-head-israeli-news-channel/00000190-49d7-d8cb-a19d-49d749d10000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战事第 262 天：哈马斯与法塔赫和解谈判无限期推迟</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-24/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-262-hamas-fatah-reconciliation-talks-postponed-indefinitely/00000190-4b22-d768-adf8-4fb279770001</link><description>总理内塔尼亚胡表示，他仍然致力于拜登上个月提出的停火协议提案，此前他因表示支持与哈马斯的“部分”协议而遭到强烈反对。 人质和失踪家庭论坛发布了以色列人赫什·戈德堡-波林被绑架的画面。利维和埃利亚·科恩 ■ 以色列国防军称，他们在加沙打死了一名哈马斯高级官员 ■ 战争开始 262 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 16:51:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-24/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-262-hamas-fatah-reconciliation-talks-postponed-indefinitely/00000190-4b22-d768-adf8-4fb279770001</guid></item><item><title>家人播放了 10 月 7 日绑架的新镜头，其中包括以色列裔美国人赫什·戈德堡-波林 (Hersh Goldberg-Polin)</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-24/ty-article/families-air-footage-of-oct-7-abductions-including-of-hersh-goldberg-polin/00000190-4a70-dafc-adb4-7bf91f040000</link><description>这段视频长约两分钟，是用恐怖分子随身携带的摄像机拍摄的。 ■ 人质家属将这段视频标记为 262 天“忽视”的证据，敦促达成协议释放人质。 ■ Hersh Goldberg-Polin、Or Levy、Elia Cohen和阿隆·奥赫尔 (Alon Ohel) 在参加新星节派对后在加沙边境附近被绑架</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 15:59:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-24/ty-article/families-air-footage-of-oct-7-abductions-including-of-hersh-goldberg-polin/00000190-4a70-dafc-adb4-7bf91f040000</guid></item></channel></rss>